data.description: Assumable VA Loan @ 2.25% Welcome to your dream home at 9 Windsor Ln NE, nestled in the heart of the highly sought-after Kenwood neighborhood in Fort Walton Beach! This impressive 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasts ample space with recent renovations. As you step through the front door, the inviting foyer guides you to a secluded office space, perfect for remote work or quiet study. Following the flow of the house, you will find a beautiful, oversized kitchen for entertaining.Beyond the kitchen lies an expansive dining and living area, providing an ideal setting for hosting friends and family. Off the living room, a private family room awaits, offering direct access to the backyard and a cozy spot for unwinding at the end of the day. Ready to enjoy the Florida sun? The property features a spectacular backyard pool and a screened-in porch, allowing you to enjoy the glorious Florida weather all year round. Have a boat? The covered carport has you covered for your boat storage needs. This home is more than just a place to live, it's a lifestyle. Don't let this incredible opportunity pass you by - schedule your personal tour today!
